### =============================================
### CATALOG ENDPOINTS
### =============================================

### Catalog - Get All Products (Paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Catalog?page=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

###

### Catalog - Get Product by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Catalog/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Catalog - Get Products by Category
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Catalog/category/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Catalog - Create Product (Admin Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Catalog
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Name"

Product Name
------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Description"

Product Description
------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Price"

99.99
------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="CategoryId"

1
------WebKitFormBoundary--

###

### Catalog - Update Product (Admin Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Catalog/update
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Id"

1
------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Name"

Updated Product Name
------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Description"

Updated Description
------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Price"

149.99
------WebKitFormBoundary--

###

### Catalog - Delete Product (Admin Only)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/Catalog/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### =============================================
### INVENTORY ENDPOINTS
### =============================================

### Inventory - Get All Inventories
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Inventory
Accept: application/json

###

### Inventory - Get Inventory by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Inventory/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Inventory - Create Inventory (Requires Auth)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Inventory
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 1,
  "quantity": 100
}

###

### Inventory - Update Inventory
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/Inventory/1?count=10&increased=true
Accept: application/json

###

### Inventory - Delete Inventory (Requires Auth)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/Inventory/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### =============================================
### ORDER ENDPOINTS
### =============================================

### Order - Index
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Order
Accept: application/json

